games.description: Keno - the classic lottery-style casino game! Pick your lucky numbers from 1 to 40, choose your risk level, and watch as 10 numbers are drawn. Match more numbers for bigger wins! With three risk levels (Easy, Medium, High), you control your destiny. Easy mode offers more frequent small wins, while High mode delivers rare but massive payouts up to 10,000x your bet!

Chicken Road 2.0 — a crazy dash where only the brave cross the road! 
 Escape the insane traffic! Twice the adrenaline!
Jump across the busy highway, dodge cars and trucks — the chick must reach its goal at any cost!

Dynamic gameplay and excitement!
Intuitive controls, vibrant graphics, hilarious animations — a game you won't be able to put down!
Complete all levels, hit the jackpot!

Ready for the challenge? Then dive into our new Chicken Road 2.0 and prove you're the fastest and most nimble chick in the world!

Welcome to the world of Sugar Daddy - a game where every turn of the desert road increases not only your chance of winning, but also the level of temptation. A luxurious sports car, a charming girl and dynamic stakes - all this awaits you in this exciting and spicy game.
